      "score": 20,
      "comments": 4,
      "author": "Helithumper",
      "published": "2026-07-18T18:12:17Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Critical unauthenticated RCE in WordPress core allows complete site takeover; prioritize auditing core codebases and applying urgent security updates.",
        "Implement virtual patching via WAF rules and restrict access to sensitive endpoints like XML-RPC and REST API to mitigate exploit attempts.",
        "Monitor web server logs for anomalous POST requests to wp-admin or wp-includes targeting undocumented PHP execution paths or file uploads."
      ]
    },
